      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e3032"> </a>The STANDARD factory settings are as follows:
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e3034"> </a>compression: 1 and a half turns;
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e3036"> </a>rebound: 2 turns.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e3038"> </a>Spring preload: (A): 15 mm.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="Attenzione"><img class="Attenzione" width="28" height="25" style="display: inline; float: none; left: 0.0; text-align: left; top: 0.0;" src="img/warning.jpg">Warning
      </div>
      <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e3041"> </a>Set both leg adjusters on the same positions.
      </div>
